    h2 Final recommendations for implementation and use.
    p By the end of the year, our team had developed all of the essential project components that met our client’s technical requirements and stakeholder objectives. 
    p After verifying that our project functioned correctly in CME Group’s secure development environment, we were able to recommend that CME Group immediately deploy our software using our provided documentation without the need for any additional modifications.

